p-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2213120/While_We_Wait_Here/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《While We Wait Here》</em></a>是一款烹饪模拟器和厨房管理游戏，游戏中的角色突然面临着即将到来的世界末日，该游戏正在为 PC 开发。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-steam-next-fests-demos-are-a-vital-celebration-of-gamings-future-3459650">为什么 Steam Next Fest 的演示是对游戏未来的重要庆祝</a></strong></li></ul><p>在游戏中，一天的开始与其他日子一样，玩家主角到达他们工作的餐厅，打开电视，问候顾客并接受顾客的订单，并为他们烹饪食物。</p><p>然而，紧急广播在变黑之前切断了电视上的新闻台，但餐厅里的其他人似乎没有注意到。 </p><figure id="attachment_3512514" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512514" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512514" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512514" class="wp-caption-text"> “当我们在这里等待”来源：Bad Vices Games</figcaption></figure><p>他们更关注自己的问题，而玩家则专注于满足他们的要求，而周围环境却发生令人不安的变化。</p><p>开发商 Bad Vices Games 表示，不同的决定将导致不同的结局，尽管没有“游戏结束”，也没有“好”或“坏”的结局。</p><p>相反，该团队希望《<em>当我们在这里等待</em>》更多的是一种“冥想体验”，讲述当那些只是因环境而来到这里的陌生人必须接受自己的死亡时会发生什么。</p><p>虽然该游戏预计将于 2024 年发布，但可以通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-steam-next-fests-demos-are-a-vital-celebration-of-gamings-future-3459650">Steam Next Fest</a>获得免费演示，该演示将持续到 10 月 16 日。 </p><figure id="attachment_3512515" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512515" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512515" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/while-we-wait-here-apocalyptic-kitchen-and-cooking-game-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512515" class="wp-caption-text"> “当我们在这里等待”来源：Bad Vices Games</figcaption></figure><p>通过演示，Bad Vices Games 将欢迎粉丝反馈，为<em>《While We Wait Here》</em>的开发及其管理机制细节和心理恐怖之间的平衡提供信息。</p><p>该开发商也是<em>《Ravenous Devils》</em>的开发团队，这是一款受<em>《理发师陶德》</em>启发的管理模拟器，玩家通过抢劫和谋杀顾客来经营一家裁缝店和酒吧。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ubisoft-says-xdefiant-indefinite-delay-was-a-hard-decision-3512449">推迟<em>XDefiant</em>对育碧来说是一个“艰难的决定”，</a>尽管它最近允许玩家在公开会议上进行测试。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cooking-sim-while-we-wait-here-is-set-at-a-diner-at-the-end-of-the-world-3512499">以世界尽头的一家小餐馆为背景的烹饪模拟游戏“While We Wait Here”</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
